Rating: 3
This is my recipe from Bon Appetit a long time (and different last name) ago. My mother used to serve it as a side dish with Dolphin Almandine and wild rice. We did not drain the tomatoes (left them soupy) and the original recipe did not call for olive oil. Bon Appetit added that. Hope you enjoy it! Gina

