Rating: 3
Depends how you like your tomato salads and with what you are serving it with. It is important to add olives (if you like them)as well as the mozz cheese cubes. Sometimes a little more sugar goes a long way. If you like it spicy add some hot peppers (hot). It depends on your taste!

